OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry. Then the rest of the
OL,7,Fnight will be dry with clear periods
OL,8,Fand the chance of some misty low cloud.
OL,9,
OL,10,CThursday:FA dry day with some sunshine
OL,11,Falthough with the chance of some
OL,12,Fpatchy low cloud. Quite warm across
OL,13,FOrkney.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry and
OL,16,Fbright on Friday. Cloudier over the
OL,17,Fweekend with a chance of showers,
OL,18,Fespecially on Saturday.
